snippet.async_client:
import asyncio

from seed import AsyncSeedPathParameters

client = AsyncSeedPathParameters(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)


async def main() -> None:
    await client.user.get_organization(
        organization_id="organizationId",
    )


asyncio.run(main())
